OL,3,CEnvironment Secretary demands answers
OL,4,Cover Camber Sands plastic pollution
OL,6,FThe Environment Secretary has called
OL,7,Ffor a full investigation after
OL,8,Fthousands of plastic pellets washed up
OL,9,Fon beaches along the south coast.
OL,11,FThe spill at Camber Sands, in East
OL,12,FSussex, has been described as one of
OL,13,Fthe worst incidents of pollution, by
OL,14,Fmonitoring group Strandliners.
OL,16,FClean-up teams and volunteers are
OL,17,Fstill working to remove the tiny beads
OL,18,Fmore than a week after they first
OL,19,Fappeared.
