OL,3,CEnvironment Secretary demands answers
OL,4,Cover Camber Sands plastic pollution
OL,6,FSouthern Water has apologised,
OL,7,Fconfirming the pellets - known as bio-
OL,8,Fbeads - escaped from its Eastbourne
OL,9,Fwastewater treatment works during
OL,10,Fheavy rainfall.
OL,12,FThe company said a filter failed,
OL,13,Fallowing the beads, which are used in
OL,14,Fthe water treatment process, to enter
OL,15,Fthe sea.
