OL,3,CEnvironment Secretary demands answers
OL,4,Cover Camber Sands plastic pollution
OL,6,FIn Parliament, Eastbourne MP Josh
OL,7,FBabarinde criticised the water company
OL,8,Fover what he called "catastrophic
OL,9,Ffailures," adding that the incident
OL,10,Ffollowed "a stench stinking out" the
OL,11,Ftown.
OL,13,FHe urged ministers to take action to
OL,14,F"force Southern Water to finally get a
OL,15,Fgrip of their appalling failures."
OL,17,FEnvironment Secretary Emma Reynolds
OL,18,Ftold MPs she was "appalled" by the
OL,19,Fpollution and said Southern Water
OL,20,Fwould be held to account.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
