OL,3,CEnvironment Secretary demands answers
OL,4,Cover Camber Sands plastic pollution
OL,6,F"There needs to be a thorough
OL,7,Finvestigation of what happened," she
OL,8,Fsaid. "Our immediate priority is to
OL,9,Faddress the damage caused ` but we
OL,10,Falso need to ask questions about why
OL,11,Fthis wasn't uncovered earlier."
OL,13,FSouthern Water said less than 10
OL,14,Ftonnes of beads were released and that
OL,15,Fits staff are continuing to assist
OL,16,Fwith the clean-up.
OL,18,F"We are very sorry this has happened
OL,19,Fand are doing everything possible to
OL,20,Finvestigate and resolve the problem,"
OL,21,Fthe company said in a statement.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
