OL,6,FRother District Council, which is
OL,7,Fleading the clean-up, has been working
OL,8,Fwith environmental experts and local
OL,9,Fvolunteers.
OL,11,FCouncil leader Doug Oliver praised the
OL,12,Fcommunity effort but said more support
OL,13,Fand specialist equipment are needed.
