OL,3,CEnvironment Secretary demands answers
OL,4,Cover Camber Sands plastic pollution
OL,6,F"I'm really proud of the very quick
OL,7,Fresponse by our officers to this awful
OL,8,Fpollution incident," Oliver said. "But
OL,9,Ffor them and our volunteers to
OL,10,Fcontinue their huge task, they need
OL,11,Ffurther equipment and support - and
OL,12,Fwe're now in talks with Southern Water
OL,13,Fto get that delivered to Camber as
OL,14,Fsoon as possible."
OL,16,FThe Environment Agency is also
OL,17,Finvolved in the investigation as
OL,18,Fconcerns grow over the long-term
OL,19,Fimpact of the pellets on marine life
OL,20,Fand local ecosystems.
